_sText:
This map is a city style map (streets, shops, cars etc) and is set in daytime it was created for use with gungame but can be used with deathmatch and other game modes too, give it a try i have created several contact points and sniper points in this map so it is good for both close and sniper combat, this is a beta release becouse it needs testing by the public who can report problems and sugest improvements. please comment critically and do not just say things like (i dnt like or it good) please give reasons for your comments as this will help me improve the map.

have fun...

shady-syler
